# generated
# NOTE: backend/drizzle/meta/ is intentionally NOT ignored — the migration
# journal must ship alongside the tracked drizzle/*.sql so a fresh clone can
# migrate (the runner drift-checks journal vs .sql and refuses to start otherwise).
